{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "c5fe3832-de2b-48de-88c5-c900a0220009", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/c5fe3832-de2b-48de-88c5-c900a0220009@1.pkg/1772597713979/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597715106", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/c5fe3832-de2b-48de-88c5-c900a0220009@1.pkg/1772597713979/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597715106"}, "identifier": "c5fe3832-de2b-48de-88c5-c900a0220009", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>本题考查 &ldquo;正确看待顺境和逆境&rdquo; 的知识点。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>B：顾方舟在逆境中不放弃、在顺境中不停步，体现了对待顺境应保持警醒（找不足）、对待逆境应积极突破（寻出路）的正确态度，符合知识点，B 正确；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>A：&ldquo;顺境必然使人骄傲&rdquo; 错误，顺境中能否保持进取取决于个人态度，并非必然骄傲；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>C：&ldquo;转化是自动发生的&rdquo; 错误，顺境与逆境的转化需要个人的主动作为，而非自然发生；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>D：&ldquo;只有经历过逆境才能把握顺境&rdquo; 绝对化，能否在顺境中把握方向与是否经历逆境无必然联系，关键在于个人的认知和态度；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>答案选 B。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（原创）&ldquo;中国脊髓灰质炎疫苗研制先驱&rdquo; 顾方舟，在研究初期面临资金短缺、实验条件简陋等逆境，却从未放弃；后期疫苗研制成功、获得广泛认可时，他也未止步，始终致力于优化疫苗效果。他曾说：&ldquo;科研路上没有一劳永逸，顺境时要找不足，逆境时要寻突破。&rdquo; 顾方舟的言行启示我们（ ）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（原创）“中国脊髓灰质炎疫苗研制先驱” 顾方舟，在研究初期面临资金短缺、实验条件简陋等逆境，却从未放弃；后期疫苗研制成功、获得广泛认可时，他也未止步，始终致力于优化疫苗效果。他曾说：“科研路上没有一劳永逸，顺境时要找不足，逆境时要寻突破。” 顾方舟的言行启示我们（ ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/c5fe3832-de2b-48de-88c5-c900a0220009@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754984697943", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">顺境必然使人骄傲自满，逆境才能让人进步</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">顺境中要保持警醒、正视不足，逆境中要积极寻找出路</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">逆境与顺境的转化是自动发生的，无需个人努力</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">只有经历过逆境的人，才能在顺境中把握方向</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（原创）&ldquo;中国脊髓灰质炎疫苗研制先驱&rdquo; 顾方舟，在研究初期面临资金短缺、实验